snippet.title: Gore Crush Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Crush body parts together in this gory soft physics puzzle game. Create disgusting combos as your smash together like body parts keeping your bloody abattoir from overflowing as you chase ever higher scores.

Available on Itch.io and Atari VCS now.

Come to Steam and other platforms November 2024

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3208710/Gore_Crush/
Itch.io: https://gigatank3000.itch.io/gore-crush
